@startuml sequence_faq_page
!theme plain
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center

title FAQ Page with Category Grouping [L2-011]
caption Visitor views /faq — FAQs grouped by category with accordion

actor Visitor
participant "Next.js Router" as Router
participant "FAQPage\n(Server Component)\napp/(storefront)/faq/page.tsx" as FaqPage
participant "FAQs API\napp/api/content/faqs/route.ts" as API
participant "Drizzle ORM" as Drizzle
database "PostgreSQL\ncontent.faqs" as DB
participant "FAQList\n(Client Component)\nlib/features/faq-list.tsx" as FaqList

== Page Load ==

Visitor -> Router: GET /faq
Router -> FaqPage: Render

FaqPage -> API: fetch("/api/content/faqs",\n{ cache: "no-store" })
API -> Drizzle: db.select().from(faqs)
Drizzle -> DB: SELECT * FROM content.faqs
DB --> Drizzle: FAQ[]
Drizzle --> API: FAQ[]
API --> FaqPage: 200 OK — FAQ[]

FaqPage -> FaqList: <FAQList faqs={faqs} />\n(Server → Client handoff via props)

FaqList -> FaqList: Group FAQs by category:\n• General\n• Products\n• Orders

FaqList --> Visitor: Render SectionHeader\n+ category groups\n+ accordion items\n(all collapsed initially)

== User Interaction ==

Visitor -> FaqList: Click FAQ question
FaqList -> FaqList: useState: setOpenId(faq.id)
FaqList --> Visitor: Expand answer panel\nRotate ChevronDown icon 180°

Visitor -> FaqList: Click same question
FaqList -> FaqList: useState: setOpenId(null)
FaqList --> Visitor: Collapse answer panel\nReset ChevronDown icon

Visitor -> FaqList: Click different question
FaqList -> FaqList: useState: setOpenId(newFaq.id)\n(previous auto-closes)
FaqList --> Visitor: Close previous,\nopen new answer panel

@enduml
